.\" kilonode/docs/man/kilonode-store.1
.Dd May 26, 2026
.Dt KILONODE-STORE 1
.Os
.Sh NAME
.Nm kilonode-store
.Nd check and maintain a KiloNode message store
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.Nm
.Fl -store Ar path
.Ar command
.Op Ar arguments
.Sh DESCRIPTION
.Nm
performs read-only checks and safe maintenance operations for a
KiloNode-native message store.
.Sh OPTIONS
.Bl -tag -width Ds
.It Fl -store Ar path
Use the message store rooted at
.Ar path .
.It Fl -help
Show command usage.
.El
.Sh COMMANDS
.Bl -tag -width Ds
.It Cm check
Report integrity findings.
.It Cm repair
Apply safe repairs.
.It Cm reindex
Rebuild indexes.
.It Cm stats
Print store counts.
.It Cm purge-deleted
Physically remove soft-deleted messages.
.It Cm export Ar dest
Create a KiloNode-native directory snapshot.
.El
.Sh FILES
.Bl -tag -width Ds
.It Pa var/messages/.kilonode-store.lock
Store lock file.
.El
.Sh EXAMPLES
.Dl kilonode-store --store /tmp/kilonode-msg-test check
.Dl kilonode-store --store /tmp/kilonode-msg-test export /tmp/kilonode-msg-export
.Sh SECURITY NOTES
Maintenance commands should run as the same user that owns the store. Export
destinations should not be inside the source store.
.Sh SEE ALSO
.Xr kilonode-msg 1 ,
.Xr kilonode-user 1
